hero.title: Hey, I'm Max!
hero.p0: Software engineer by day, badminton and rock climbing enthusiast by night
hero.des0: I'm a 2th year computer science student at the University of Western Ontario and I specialize in software engineering. I've a strong desire to improve my skills and learn as much as I can.
hero.des1: I enjoy working in efficient team environments to create high-quality and impactful code. My strongest tech stack includes Python, Java, TypeScript, React, and Next.js. I value a supportive company culture and clear communication. I hope I would be able to integrate myself as part of your team easily!
